    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黄衣婴儿》是一款克系滑稽恐怖游戏，你需要照看一个可疑的婴儿，并躲过他夺取控制权的尝试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏的11个章节里，你必须保证这个小疯子吃得饱、勤洗澡，并且最重要的是，还要哄得好。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291340/extras/39999db01c1059e0e2b2ad51a9afeadd.poster.avif?t=1763401770\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291340/extras/39999db01c1059e0e2b2ad51a9afeadd.webm?t=1763401770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291340/extras/39999db01c1059e0e2b2ad51a9afeadd.mp4?t=1763401770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>悉心照料</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这可能不是你第一次带孩子，但可能是最后一次。所以一定要仔细听你脑海里的轻语，那个告诉你只要听话就会没事的声音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的带孩子职责</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >给孩子喂食</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清洗尿布</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝不要把他放进烤箱</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >给他讲睡前故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做芝士烤三明治</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哄他入睡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不能走开</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291340/extras/a1047c762fd2122c1078394908c6f1e2.poster.avif?t=1763401770\" width=614 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291340/extras/a1047c762fd2122c1078394908c6f1e2.webm?t=1763401770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291340/extras/a1047c762fd2122c1078394908c6f1e2.mp4?t=1763401770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Hastur并不总是喜欢早睡</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >亮点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个“可爱的”婴儿布娃娃（反正轻语是这么告诉我们的）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3幕神秘故事等待你解开</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >足以让你失去理智的棘手谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >稳定无害、完全可预测的环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >激烈的追逐过场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等你寻找和解救的受困灵魂 - 解锁像大头模式这样的作弊招式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的灵魂有被吞噬的可能性</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291340/extras/fa77588b11f8234ada261830eb6c1b60.poster.avif?t=1763401770\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291340/extras/fa77588b11f8234ada261830eb6c1b60.webm?t=1763401770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291340/extras/fa77588b11f8234ada261830eb6c1b60.mp4?t=1763401770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>他从不睡觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《黄衣婴儿》的起源</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黄衣婴儿》最早是在48小时内为游戏制作节创作的，灵感源自罗伯特•钱伯斯的短篇故事《黄衣之王》。移动端下载次数超过1.4亿次，游戏视频在社交媒体上观看人次达数百万。</p>",
